        Api key from worldweatheronline.com for their V2 API. Required, no default.

        You can register for a key at https://developer.worldweatheronline.com/auth/register
        Parameters:

        Returns:
        this Builder for chaining
        Throws:

      • setLocation

        public Fetcher.Builder setLocation(String location)
        Location to fetch for. Required, no default.

        May be a UK or Canadian postcode, US zip code, name of a city, IPv4 address (in dotted quad notation) or Latitude, Longitude pair (decimal degrees, comma separated)
        Parameters:
        location - String name of the location. The API will work out the type from context.
